after suffering from neck pain for years, Dr. Reyfman offered cervical epidural injections and then a cervical discectomy;
the results have been amazing: I can turn my head without pain, and I am no longer on constant medication;
the procedure went well, and I really appreciated how much care and attention the team gave me throughout my visits;
